# Door UI (Shadcn only)

- Import UI only from `@/components/ui/*` (Button, Input, Dialog, Card, etc.).
- Never add `@radix-ui/*` imports outside `apps/door/src/components/ui/**`. Radix is an implementation detail of the Shadcn primitive layer only.
- Prefer Shadcn wrappers over raw HTML controls (`<button>`, `<input>`, `<select>`, `<textarea>`).
- Do not use HeroUI or other component libraries in door (`apps/web` uses HeroUI; door uses Shadcn like admin).
